{
  "video_id": "z1r1ugmDxjk",
  "title": "How art can shape America's conversation about freedom | Dread Scott",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12858.0,
      "end_time": 14333.0,
      "text": "I am a visual artist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14357.0,
      "end_time": 17738.0,
      "text": "and I make revolutionary art to propel history forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18369.0,
      "end_time": 20780.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to come right out and tell you something:"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20804.0,
      "end_time": 22668.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t accept the economic foundation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22693.0,
      "end_time": 23854.0,
      "text": "the social relations"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23878.0,
      "end_time": 25578.0,
      "text": "or the governing ideas of America."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26523.0,
      "end_time": 28457.0,
      "text": "My art contributes to fundamental change"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28481.0,
      "end_time": 32360.0,
      "text": "by encouraging an audience to address big questions from that perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32892.0,
      "end_time": 36178.0,
      "text": "Social change is hard, but ideas matter tremendously."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37594.0,
      "end_time": 40714.0,
      "text": "When I say I&#39;m an artist, most people think, \"Oh, he&#39;s a painter.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40738.0,
      "end_time": 43271.0,
      "text": "Behind me, you can see some of the kind of work I do."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43295.0,
      "end_time": 45632.0,
      "text": "\"Imagine a World Without America\" is a painting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45656.0,
      "end_time": 47149.0,
      "text": "but I work in a range of media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47173.0,
      "end_time": 50173.0,
      "text": "including photography, video and performance art."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53536.0,
      "end_time": 56354.0,
      "text": "A current project, \"Slave Rebellion Reenactment,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56378.0,
      "end_time": 59354.0,
      "text": "is going to be reenacted on the outskirts of New Orleans"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59378.0,
      "end_time": 60537.0,
      "text": "this November."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62500.0,
      "end_time": 66379.0,
      "text": "In 1989, I had an artwork that became the center of controversy"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66403.0,
      "end_time": 69510.0,
      "text": "over its transgressive use of the American flag."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69620.0,
      "end_time": 72254.0,
      "text": "\"What is the Proper Way to Display a US Flag?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72278.0,
      "end_time": 75352.0,
      "text": "is a conceptual work that encouraged audience participation."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 76300.0,
      "end_time": 78700.0,
      "text": "It consisted of a photo montage that had text that read,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78724.0,
      "end_time": 81219.0,
      "text": "\"What is the Proper Way to Display a US Flag?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81243.0,
      "end_time": 84841.0,
      "text": "Below that were books that people could write responses to that question in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84865.0,
      "end_time": 88620.0,
      "text": "and below that was a flag that people had the option of standing on."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88860.0,
      "end_time": 91146.0,
      "text": "The photo montage consisted of images of South Korean students"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91170.0,
      "end_time": 92617.0,
      "text": "burning American flags,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92641.0,
      "end_time": 95465.0,
      "text": "holding signs that said, \"Yankee go home. Son of a bitch,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95489.0,
      "end_time": 98728.0,
      "text": "and below that were flag-draped coffins coming back from Vietnam."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 99461.0,
      "end_time": 101529.0,
      "text": "People wrote long and short answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101553.0,
      "end_time": 105950.0,
      "text": "Thousands of people engaged with the work in a lot of different languages."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105420.0,
      "end_time": 106715.0,
      "text": "Some of the people said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107414.0,
      "end_time": 108668.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m a German girl."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 108692.0,
      "end_time": 111714.0,
      "text": "If we Germans would admire our flag as you all do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 111738.0,
      "end_time": 113473.0,
      "text": "we would be called Nazis again."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 113497.0,
      "end_time": 116103.0,
      "text": "I think you do have too much trouble about this flag.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117930.0,
      "end_time": 120762.0,
      "text": "\"I think that the artist should be returned to his heritage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 120786.0,
      "end_time": 122431.0,
      "text": "i.e., the jungles of Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122455.0,
      "end_time": 125810.0,
      "text": "and then he can shovel manure in his artistic way.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 126981.0,
      "end_time": 130582.0,
      "text": "\"This flag I&#39;m standing on stands for everything oppressive in this system:"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130606.0,
      "end_time": 133674.0,
      "text": "the murder of the Indians and all the oppressed around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 133698.0,
      "end_time": 135702.0,
      "text": "including my brother who was shot by a pig,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 135726.0,
      "end_time": 138762.0,
      "text": "who kicked over his body to &#39;make sure the nigger was dead.&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139776.0,
      "end_time": 141379.0,
      "text": "That pig was wearing the flag."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141403.0,
      "end_time": 143745.0,
      "text": "Thank you, Dread Scott, for this opportunity.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144259.0,
      "end_time": 145859.0,
      "text": "\"As a veteran defending the flag,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 145884.0,
      "end_time": 148153.0,
      "text": "I personally would never defend your stupid ass!"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148177.0,
      "end_time": 150695.0,
      "text": "You should be shot!\" -- US Navy Seal Team."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 152463.0,
      "end_time": 155924.0,
      "text": "As you can see, people had very strong reactions about the flag then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 155949.0,
      "end_time": 157180.0,
      "text": "as they do now."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 157606.0,
      "end_time": 161390.0,
      "text": "There were demonstrations of veterans in front of the Art Institute of Chicago."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 161414.0,
      "end_time": 162662.0,
      "text": "They chanted things like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 162687.0,
      "end_time": 164935.0,
      "text": "\"The flag and the artist, hang them both high,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 164959.0,
      "end_time": 166483.0,
      "text": "evoking images of lynching."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 166507.0,
      "end_time": 168145.0,
      "text": "I received numerous death threats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 168169.0,
      "end_time": 170299.0,
      "text": "and bomb threats were phoned in to my school."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 170323.0,
      "end_time": 172300.0,
      "text": "It was a very dangerous situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 172401.0,
      "end_time": 174934.0,
      "text": "Later, President Bush called the work \"disgraceful,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 174958.0,
      "end_time": 176753.0,
      "text": "which I viewed as a tremendous honor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 176777.0,
      "end_time": 178302.0,
      "text": "and Congress outlawed the work."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 178326.0,
      "end_time": 179430.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 179455.0,
      "end_time": 183472.0,
      "text": "I became part of a Supreme Court case when I and others defied that law,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 183496.0,
      "end_time": 185681.0,
      "text": "by burning flags on the steps of the Capitol."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 186485.0,
      "end_time": 189605.0,
      "text": "That action and the subsequent legal and political battle"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189629.0,
      "end_time": 193307.0,
      "text": "led to a landmark First Amendment decision that prevented the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 193331.0,
      "end_time": 195709.0,
      "text": "from demanding patriotism be mandatory."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 196169.0,
      "end_time": 197389.0,
      "text": "But let me back up a bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 197413.0,
      "end_time": 199673.0,
      "text": "These people literally wanted me dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 200633.0,
      "end_time": 203257.0,
      "text": "What I would do at this moment would make a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 203281.0,
      "end_time": 205328.0,
      "text": "This is me at the exact same moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 205352.0,
      "end_time": 207133.0,
      "text": "eight stories above that crowd."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 208368.0,
      "end_time": 210249.0,
      "text": "It was supposed to be for a photo shoot"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 210273.0,
      "end_time": 214670.0,
      "text": "that was going to take place on the steps where the veterans were at that time."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 214920.0,
      "end_time": 217118.0,
      "text": "It wouldn&#39;t have been safe for me to be there, to say the least."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 217142.0,
      "end_time": 219283.0,
      "text": "But it was really important to do that shoot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 219307.0,
      "end_time": 222196.0,
      "text": "because while some wanted to kill me, it was also a situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 222220.0,
      "end_time": 225910.0,
      "text": "where those who viewed the American flag as standing for everything oppressive"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 225934.0,
      "end_time": 227900.0,
      "text": "in this system"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 227114.0,
      "end_time": 228409.0,
      "text": "felt that they had a voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 228433.0,
      "end_time": 230400.0,
      "text": "and that voice needed to be amplified."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 230837.0,
      "end_time": 232600.0,
      "text": "The point is this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 232850.0,
      "end_time": 233455.0,
      "text": "changing anything --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 233479.0,
      "end_time": 237481.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s conventional ideas about US national symbols,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 237505.0,
      "end_time": 240427.0,
      "text": "traditional thinking challenged by scientific breakthroughs"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 240451.0,
      "end_time": 242879.0,
      "text": "or ousting an authoritarian president --"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 242903.0,
      "end_time": 244230.0,
      "text": "requires a lot of things."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 244254.0,
      "end_time": 245866.0,
      "text": "It requires courage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 245890.0,
      "end_time": 247450.0,
      "text": "luck"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 247690.0,
      "end_time": 249713.0,
      "text": "and also vision and boldness of action."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 250971.0,
      "end_time": 252141.0,
      "text": "But on luck --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 252165.0,
      "end_time": 255638.0,
      "text": "I have to say, the photo shoot we did might not have worked out so well."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 255662.0,
      "end_time": 258910.0,
      "text": "We laughed after we were out of the area."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 258116.0,
      "end_time": 259983.0,
      "text": "But the thing is, it was worth the risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 260700.0,
      "end_time": 262150.0,
      "text": "because of the stakes that were involved."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 262390.0,
      "end_time": 264192.0,
      "text": "And in this case, the luck led to a wonderful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 264216.0,
      "end_time": 265727.0,
      "text": "profound and powerful situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 265751.0,
      "end_time": 267217.0,
      "text": "that was also humorous."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 267241.0,
      "end_time": 268405.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 268429.0,
      "end_time": 270804.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}